        <p class="body-text dark-text a4" style="margin-top:1rem;">New event. New job. New menu. Each means a designer, a print run, separate social posts, a separate email, a separate WhatsApp — all disconnected, all manual, all expensive.</p>
        <div class="pull-quote dark a5" style="margin-top:1.5rem;font-size:1rem;">"The same content, rebuilt<br/>five times for five different surfaces."</div>
