            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--mid);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;flex-shrink:0;"></div>Design a poster — Canva or freelancer</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--mid);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;flex-shrink:0;"></div>Separate graphic for Instagram</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--mid);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;flex-shrink:0;"></div>Manual WhatsApp draft and send</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--mid);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;flex-shrink:0;"></div>No QR tracking — no data on what works</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--mid);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;flex-shrink:0;"></div>Menu reprinted every time a price changes</div>
