            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--dark);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);flex-shrink:0;"></div>Menu updated live — print, screen, digital</div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--dark);"><div style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);flex-shrink:0;"></div>Scan data by placement — know what works</div>
